CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 6 reads: "10. Winners of the adult cake-baking contest, left to right, Mrs. Beatrice Hall, first prize; Mrs. Lillie Harris, second; Mrs. Ida Rivers, third, and Mrs. Louis Walker, fourth prize."
TitMainTitle: Contest winners Beatrice Hall, Lillie Harris, Ida Rivers, and Louis Walker holding cakes in Westinghouse kitchen booth in Syria Mosque for the 1958 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
